WEBVTT

00:00:25.211 --> 00:00:26.629
I love you.

00:00:28.965 --> 00:00:30.648
You didn’t even read
the whole thing.

00:00:31.176 --> 00:00:32.273
Okay?

00:00:33.470 --> 00:00:34.446
Much better.

00:00:34.471 --> 00:00:35.764
I’m your only best friend.

00:00:35.764 --> 00:00:36.823
Of course.

00:00:36.848 --> 00:00:38.116
Welcome to college!

00:00:38.141 --> 00:00:39.225
I missed you guys.

00:00:40.477 --> 00:00:43.563
Do you like anyone
in your college?

00:00:43.734 --> 00:00:45.152
I don’t like any of them.

00:00:46.024 --> 00:00:47.164
You?

00:00:47.609 --> 00:00:49.944
I’m asking you. Do you like
anyone at your school yet?

00:00:49.944 --> 00:00:52.697
You didn’t know about
Arkin’s photoshoot, did you?

00:00:52.884 --> 00:00:54.062
I’m so stupid.

00:00:54.157 --> 00:00:55.492
You’re not stupid.

00:00:56.743 --> 00:00:57.952
You just like the guy.

00:01:00.246 --> 00:01:02.791
He wanted to
confess his feelings,

00:01:02.791 --> 00:01:04.751
but couldn’t
because they’re friends.

00:01:04.751 --> 00:01:06.211
What if I told you—

00:01:06.211 --> 00:01:07.378
I love you.

00:01:07.378 --> 00:01:08.755
Of course, you love me.

00:01:09.297 --> 00:01:11.633
We’re friends, right?

00:01:11.925 --> 00:01:13.651
I want to keep you all to myself.

00:01:13.676 --> 00:01:14.569
Mama.

00:01:14.594 --> 00:01:17.125
Didn’t I tell you not to
bother me when I’m writing?

00:01:19.599 --> 00:01:21.351
You’ll leave me, too.

00:02:37.510 --> 00:02:38.678
Via, I bought pizza.

00:02:42.098 --> 00:02:43.111
Via?

00:02:44.017 --> 00:02:45.166
What happened to you?

00:02:46.186 --> 00:02:47.189
Why?

00:02:48.897 --> 00:02:50.690
Why didn’t you tell me?

00:03:06.080 --> 00:03:07.582
You’ll leave me, too.

00:03:11.961 --> 00:03:13.313
No.

00:03:13.338 --> 00:03:14.589
I’m never leaving you.

00:03:14.797 --> 00:03:15.398
Okay?

00:03:15.423 --> 00:03:16.564
I’m really sorry.

00:03:17.008 --> 00:03:18.197
I’m sorry.

00:03:20.384 --> 00:03:22.094
You’ll change, too.

00:03:23.932 --> 00:03:26.017
You won’t have time for me, too.

00:03:26.017 --> 00:03:28.061
You’ll stop caring about me.

00:03:28.853 --> 00:03:30.980
You’ll leave me
just like she did.

00:03:32.690 --> 00:03:34.192
No. No, I won’t.

00:03:34.484 --> 00:03:35.627
Via, listen.

00:03:35.652 --> 00:03:37.170
No matter what happens,

00:03:37.195 --> 00:03:38.529
I’m not going anywhere.

00:03:39.113 --> 00:03:40.240
I’m sorry I didn’t tell you

00:03:40.240 --> 00:03:44.160
because I was scared you
might feel the same pain

00:03:44.160 --> 00:03:45.286
you felt before.

00:03:45.453 --> 00:03:46.913
Okay? I’m sorry.

00:03:46.913 --> 00:03:48.009
I’m really sorry.

00:03:48.373 --> 00:03:50.333
Kino, do you even know
how many times

00:03:50.333 --> 00:03:54.545
I wished Mama was still here
to take care of me?

00:03:56.839 --> 00:04:00.510
I wish I had a normal life
like you all do.

00:04:03.346 --> 00:04:06.224
I wish I didn’t have
to think about

00:04:06.224 --> 00:04:11.145
all the responsibilities
I have for my siblings.

00:04:13.690 --> 00:04:18.069
Kino, I wish I weren’t this tired.

00:04:23.199 --> 00:04:26.452
If only she hadn’t gone
into show business,

00:04:26.452 --> 00:04:28.538
she would still be here with me.

00:04:28.538 --> 00:04:31.499
I wish she were
still here today.

00:04:35.837 --> 00:04:37.213
I know, Via.

00:04:37.755 --> 00:04:41.009
Okay? Please, I’m sorry.

00:04:43.511 --> 00:04:45.263
I’m sorry. Please…

00:04:53.730 --> 00:04:55.273
Kino, she died.

00:04:56.774 --> 00:04:59.193
She knew she had
a kidney problem

00:04:59.193 --> 00:05:00.653
because she kept
taking those pills,

00:05:00.653 --> 00:05:01.904
but what did she do?

00:05:01.904 --> 00:05:04.532
She didn’t take care of herself.

00:05:06.868 --> 00:05:08.411
Why?

00:05:11.080 --> 00:05:13.958
Why was it so easy
for her to leave me?

00:05:13.958 --> 00:05:16.836
Why was it so easy for her
to leave all of us?

00:05:16.836 --> 00:05:19.505
Didn’t she love us?

00:05:21.382 --> 00:05:23.426
Kino, why was it
so easy for her

00:05:23.426 --> 00:05:26.471
to dump everything on me?

00:05:30.266 --> 00:05:31.726
Via, I don’t think
that’s how it was.

00:05:31.726 --> 00:05:34.896
Your mom was kind, and
she loved all of you.

00:05:35.813 --> 00:05:38.816
You don’t know how I felt.

00:05:40.193 --> 00:05:42.362
Instead of playing,

00:05:42.362 --> 00:05:46.074
I was carrying my crying
sibling in my arms,

00:05:46.074 --> 00:05:49.035
and you know what
Mama was doing then?

00:05:49.035 --> 00:05:53.623
Mama was right there,
busy with her music.

00:05:55.750 --> 00:05:58.294
How important is that to you all?

00:05:58.294 --> 00:06:02.830
All that fucking attention,
Kino, and for what?

00:06:03.132 --> 00:06:07.428
Can’t you live without it?

00:06:12.892 --> 00:06:13.893
Via…

00:06:14.936 --> 00:06:15.937
Via.

00:06:20.024 --> 00:06:21.067
Via, I need to do this.

00:06:21.067 --> 00:06:22.360
Please, you have to understand.

00:06:22.360 --> 00:06:23.853
But why?

00:06:24.821 --> 00:06:26.030
Do you know how many times

00:06:26.055 --> 00:06:29.649
Mama came home after
people threw things at her?

00:06:29.674 --> 00:06:32.829
Those same people
who adored her

00:06:32.829 --> 00:06:33.788
when she was on top,

00:06:33.788 --> 00:06:37.041
but stepped all over her
when she was down.

00:06:38.584 --> 00:06:41.045
Kino, that hurt so much.

00:06:43.297 --> 00:06:46.801
Do you know how painful
it was to witness that?

00:06:49.999 --> 00:06:51.033
Kino…

00:06:54.934 --> 00:06:56.579
Kino, I won’t be able
to handle it

00:06:56.604 --> 00:06:58.481
if that happens to you.

00:07:00.356 --> 00:07:02.316
Kino, I don’t want you
to get hurt.

00:07:02.316 --> 00:07:06.154
I can’t watch you suffer.

00:07:07.155 --> 00:07:11.576
Why do you keep putting yourself
under that spotlight?

00:07:11.601 --> 00:07:16.105
Can’t you just focus
on your studies instead?

00:07:16.613 --> 00:07:19.408
Via, I know that pain.

00:07:19.876 --> 00:07:22.253
Mama went through that too, but—

00:07:27.467 --> 00:07:29.093
I still want to do this.

00:07:29.093 --> 00:07:30.595
I really want this.

00:07:33.222 --> 00:07:37.226
This can help my name if I want
to get into the film industry.

00:07:37.393 --> 00:07:38.426
Via—

00:07:39.279 --> 00:07:41.948
Via, I’m thinking
about my future too.

00:07:44.066 --> 00:07:46.277
This is good for
my career, so please

00:07:46.277 --> 00:07:48.446
don’t stop me from doing this.

00:07:58.831 --> 00:07:59.832
I’m sorry.

00:08:01.083 --> 00:08:02.585
I’m really sorry.

00:08:03.336 --> 00:08:04.462
Please, I’m sorry.

00:08:07.507 --> 00:08:08.633
- I’m sorry.
- No.

00:08:10.301 --> 00:08:11.552
I’m sorry, Larkin.

00:08:13.554 --> 00:08:14.847
I’m sorry.

00:08:18.017 --> 00:08:19.894
I’m sorry for what I said.

00:08:19.894 --> 00:08:21.646
I shouldn’t have said that.

00:08:21.646 --> 00:08:23.064
I was wrong.

00:08:26.359 --> 00:08:29.695
I’m happy for you. I really am.

00:08:33.282 --> 00:08:34.867
Don’t worry.

00:08:38.621 --> 00:08:40.122
I’m still here.

00:08:41.999 --> 00:08:45.461
I’ll still be here,
right behind you.

00:08:46.128 --> 00:08:48.756
But Kino, don’t neglect yourself,

00:08:48.756 --> 00:08:51.133
don’t neglect your studies, okay?

00:08:52.301 --> 00:08:55.263
Being a director is still
your real dream, right?

00:09:05.606 --> 00:09:08.025
Sorry.

00:09:43.769 --> 00:09:44.793
Sweetheart?

00:09:45.730 --> 00:09:46.939
Are you all right?

00:09:48.524 --> 00:09:49.734
Did something happen?

00:10:00.244 --> 00:10:01.454
Are you still upset?

00:10:03.664 --> 00:10:06.457
Are you still not visiting
your mom this year?

00:10:13.674 --> 00:10:14.785
You know, sweetheart,

00:10:15.760 --> 00:10:18.346
your mom loved you,
even if she’s gone.

00:10:20.891 --> 00:10:22.393
You never fell short for her.

00:10:25.353 --> 00:10:27.313
Until her last breath,

00:10:28.564 --> 00:10:31.525
she was looking for you
and your siblings.

00:10:35.905 --> 00:10:39.367
If I could apologize for
everything she did, I would.

00:10:42.495 --> 00:10:43.913
I’m sorry, Via.

00:10:44.497 --> 00:10:46.957
You had to carry all
that weight on your back.

00:10:48.042 --> 00:10:49.293
But don’t worry.

00:10:50.336 --> 00:10:53.631
Papa’s here to help you
carry everything.

00:10:57.551 --> 00:11:00.096
Everything you’ve done
for your siblings.

00:11:00.206 --> 00:11:01.416
Even for Arkin.

00:11:03.057 --> 00:11:07.061
I know they won’t leave you
the way your mom did.

00:11:08.854 --> 00:11:10.940
And your mom
didn’t want that either.

00:11:12.191 --> 00:11:13.484
So cheer up now.

00:11:17.321 --> 00:11:18.332
Okay?

00:11:30.209 --> 00:11:31.794
Thank you, Papa.

00:11:33.546 --> 00:11:34.839
Thank you.

00:11:43.389 --> 00:11:44.402
All right.

00:11:45.182 --> 00:11:46.559
Are you okay?

00:11:48.144 --> 00:11:49.353
You need me to stay?

00:11:50.062 --> 00:11:51.439
No, I’m okay.

00:12:13.335 --> 00:12:16.297
Via? Please don’t be mad
at me anymore.

00:12:16.773 --> 00:12:20.360
I’m really sorry, Via.

00:12:26.223 --> 00:12:29.602
I’m not mad, Kino.

00:12:50.539 --> 00:12:51.749
Our project for—

00:12:51.749 --> 00:12:53.501
- I haven’t started it yet.
- Yeah, same.

00:12:53.501 --> 00:12:54.877
- I’ll do it later.
- Hey! There’s Via.

00:12:54.877 --> 00:12:56.837
Via! Have you been waiting long?

00:12:57.171 --> 00:12:59.423
Kind of. Just a bit.

00:12:59.548 --> 00:13:01.759
By the way, this is Dan.

00:13:02.802 --> 00:13:04.345
Yeah, we’ve already met.

00:13:04.845 --> 00:13:07.223
There you go.

00:13:07.223 --> 00:13:09.475
- So they already know each other.
- They know each other.

00:13:09.475 --> 00:13:10.768
He has a crush on you.

00:13:10.793 --> 00:13:12.205
Hey, idiot! No, I don’t.

00:13:12.603 --> 00:13:14.021
Don’t believe them.

00:13:14.271 --> 00:13:15.773
Look at him,
he’s being defensive.

00:13:15.798 --> 00:13:17.508
- Hi, Via.
- Hi.

00:13:18.067 --> 00:13:19.819
Hi, Via? Hi, Via?

00:13:22.696 --> 00:13:23.720
Via!

00:13:24.114 --> 00:13:26.158
Wanna hangout next week at my school?

00:13:26.207 --> 00:13:27.208
I’m free.

00:13:30.433 --> 00:13:31.501
Sure.

00:13:31.956 --> 00:13:33.332
You’re in front of your crush.

00:13:33.332 --> 00:13:34.517
Fix it.

00:13:34.542 --> 00:13:36.502
Hey, Via. They said
let’s go to the cafeteria.

00:13:36.658 --> 00:13:39.939
- Let’s go! All right, let’s go then.
- Let’s go to the cafeteria.

00:13:39.964 --> 00:13:41.590
Look at you, acting shy.

00:13:41.615 --> 00:13:42.866
Come on, Via.

00:13:43.300 --> 00:13:44.426
Seriously, this guy...

00:13:57.648 --> 00:13:58.673
Via!

00:13:59.448 --> 00:14:01.742
Sorry, my class took so long.

00:14:02.934 --> 00:14:04.004
It’s okay.

00:14:04.209 --> 00:14:05.919
So, how was your class?

00:14:06.448 --> 00:14:09.994
Can you still handle studying
and acting at the same time?

00:14:12.621 --> 00:14:13.706
I’m managing.

00:14:14.665 --> 00:14:17.293
And don’t worry.
I won’t neglect my studies.

00:14:17.835 --> 00:14:18.845
You better.

00:14:23.883 --> 00:14:26.302
Look, they’re so sweet.

00:14:27.344 --> 00:14:29.471
Is that Luna’s boyfriend, Kalix?

00:14:30.097 --> 00:14:31.156
Yeah.

00:14:31.181 --> 00:14:32.892
I feel like they’re
really meant to be.

00:14:33.434 --> 00:14:34.439
How can you tell?

00:14:36.228 --> 00:14:38.063
Luna looks different.

00:14:38.647 --> 00:14:43.193
You can see that she’s
super in love with Kalix.

00:14:46.906 --> 00:14:48.157
I wonder what that feels like.

00:14:59.543 --> 00:15:00.769
What about you?

00:15:00.794 --> 00:15:03.088
Don’t you like
anyone you work with?

00:15:03.839 --> 00:15:05.966
You’re surrounded by
so many pretty girls.

00:15:09.511 --> 00:15:11.055
Why are you asking that?

00:15:19.063 --> 00:15:20.230
Just kidding.

00:15:21.190 --> 00:15:22.291
No.

00:15:22.316 --> 00:15:23.734
I don’t like anyone there.

00:15:24.485 --> 00:15:25.069
You?

00:15:25.069 --> 00:15:26.236
Do you like anyone?

00:15:34.620 --> 00:15:37.623
You… You’re the one I like.

00:15:37.623 --> 00:15:41.585
But it can’t happen,
so being friends is enough.

00:16:02.773 --> 00:16:03.774
Hold still.

00:16:29.967 --> 00:16:31.093
By the way, Via…

00:16:31.844 --> 00:16:34.763
I might get a little busy
starting next week.

00:16:35.180 --> 00:16:36.849
I have some acting gigs lined up.

00:16:37.099 --> 00:16:38.225
They’re just small roles,

00:16:38.225 --> 00:16:41.854
but you know me,
I always do my best.

00:16:43.147 --> 00:16:46.358
Just tell me when it airs, okay?

00:16:47.234 --> 00:16:48.235
I’ll watch you.

00:16:49.570 --> 00:16:50.529
Thank you, Via.

00:16:53.782 --> 00:16:54.658
It’s so hot, Kino.

00:16:56.035 --> 00:16:56.577
It’s so hot.

00:16:56.577 --> 00:16:58.579
Is your classroom too warm?

00:16:58.912 --> 00:17:00.011
Did you even shower
this morning?

00:17:00.036 --> 00:17:01.037
You kinda stink.

00:17:01.707 --> 00:17:03.292
Do you know how expensive
my perfume is

00:17:03.292 --> 00:17:04.168
and then you’re telling me—

00:17:04.168 --> 00:17:05.044
- that I stink?
- That’s different.

00:17:05.044 --> 00:17:06.336
Perfume and deodorant
are different.

00:17:06.336 --> 00:17:07.946
My soap is expensive too, Via.

00:17:07.971 --> 00:17:09.848
I said deodorant, didn’t I?

00:17:09.923 --> 00:17:11.633
I use alum powder sometimes.

00:17:31.070 --> 00:17:32.613
So you’re okay with that scene?

00:17:32.613 --> 00:17:34.256
And you know where
it picks up from, right?

00:17:34.281 --> 00:17:36.492
For the next sequence
we’re shooting,

00:17:36.492 --> 00:17:39.828
does the director want
a big reaction from me?

00:17:39.995 --> 00:17:42.456
Maybe keep it subtle so
you don’t overshadow Paul.

00:17:42.456 --> 00:17:43.749
- But tell me, okay? When—
- Just do better next time.

00:17:43.749 --> 00:17:46.251
- Tell me if the director has any comments.
- Of course.

00:17:46.251 --> 00:17:47.086
Yeah. That’s fine.

00:17:47.086 --> 00:17:48.170
The set will be ready
in five minutes, okay?

00:17:48.170 --> 00:17:49.129
- Yes.
- Okay.

00:17:49.129 --> 00:17:50.355
Thank you.

00:17:50.380 --> 00:17:52.132
Do you have a lot of scenes?

00:17:53.092 --> 00:17:55.969
Actually, I got more scenes

00:17:55.969 --> 00:17:59.157
because the director
seems to like me.

00:17:59.681 --> 00:18:03.685
Really now? Maybe your
acting was just very good.

00:18:03.685 --> 00:18:06.230
That’s a given, but I feel
like he noticed

00:18:06.230 --> 00:18:07.815
how handsome I am. And—

00:18:09.900 --> 00:18:10.931
Hello?

00:18:12.069 --> 00:18:13.070
Via?

00:18:14.995 --> 00:18:15.996
Via!

00:18:16.406 --> 00:18:18.117
Be careful there, Kino.

00:18:18.450 --> 00:18:19.952
Darn it, we lost connection.

00:18:20.244 --> 00:18:21.245
I’ll just call later.

00:18:45.144 --> 00:18:48.230
Kino, are you home already?

00:18:57.447 --> 00:18:59.950
Not yet.
I’ll message you later,

00:18:59.950 --> 00:19:02.870
still busy with the shoot.

00:19:27.352 --> 00:19:29.735
Kino has so many friends now.

00:19:35.678 --> 00:19:37.930
I hope you’re doing okay, Ke.

00:19:38.822 --> 00:19:40.991
Thanks, the therapist
you recommended

00:19:40.991 --> 00:19:42.701
really helped me.

00:19:44.369 --> 00:19:45.579
Thank you.

00:19:45.913 --> 00:19:47.331
You guys didn’t leave me.

00:19:51.623 --> 00:19:52.958
Of course, Ke.

00:19:54.004 --> 00:19:56.798
We’re here for you,
we won’t leave you.

00:20:01.428 --> 00:20:02.512
What about you?

00:20:03.265 --> 00:20:04.599
How are you?

00:20:06.850 --> 00:20:07.899
I’m fine.

00:20:08.310 --> 00:20:10.604
She says she’s fine, but
she’s been crying nonstop.

00:20:10.604 --> 00:20:12.456
Don’t hold it in.
Go ahead, let it out.

00:20:12.481 --> 00:20:13.565
I don’t want to cry anymore.

00:20:13.565 --> 00:20:15.901
I’ve cried too much over Kalix.

00:20:15.901 --> 00:20:16.993
It’s too much.

00:20:17.110 --> 00:20:18.654
Just too much. I’m done.

00:20:19.613 --> 00:20:21.531
This is the first time
I’ve seen Luna and Ke

00:20:21.531 --> 00:20:23.909
like this because of guys.

00:20:24.188 --> 00:20:27.501
But it’s also the first time
I’ve seen them fall this hard.

00:20:27.936 --> 00:20:30.485
It’s scary when
it backfires on you.

00:20:32.542 --> 00:20:34.169
Where’s Arkin by the way?

00:20:34.419 --> 00:20:37.297
Is he still busy
with his acting gigs?

00:20:38.374 --> 00:20:41.293
Yeah. His shoots have
been nonstop ever since

00:20:41.318 --> 00:20:43.149
he got cast in that teleserye.

00:20:44.096 --> 00:20:46.682
Wow, my best friend is
really getting famous.

00:20:47.224 --> 00:20:49.268
Wow, stealing best friends now?

00:20:49.268 --> 00:20:50.435
He’s Via’s best friend.

00:20:50.435 --> 00:20:52.854
But seriously,
tell Arkin he should rest.

00:20:52.854 --> 00:20:54.516
He might get sick at this rate.

00:20:55.274 --> 00:20:57.985
Yeah, it feels like he hasn’t
checked in for a long time.

00:20:58.527 --> 00:20:59.528
You’re right.

00:20:59.903 --> 00:21:01.571
But we’re meeting later.

00:21:05.993 --> 00:21:07.327
Eat first, Ke.

00:21:08.140 --> 00:21:09.725
Kino, are we
still meeting later?

00:21:09.750 --> 00:21:11.502
I’ll stop by your school.

00:21:13.792 --> 00:21:14.793
I’ll smack you!

00:21:14.793 --> 00:21:16.920
I don’t want to cry anymore.
I’m exhausted.

00:21:22.027 --> 00:21:23.813
Kino, I’m here now.

00:21:29.971 --> 00:21:33.683
It’s been days, and
Kino’s barely been replying.

00:21:33.708 --> 00:21:35.252
I hope he’s okay.

00:21:35.277 --> 00:21:38.863
Via, aren’t you the one
who’s always with Arkin?

00:21:38.900 --> 00:21:39.543
Yeah.

00:21:39.568 --> 00:21:40.735
How is he?

00:21:41.403 --> 00:21:42.612
Is he not coming back?

00:21:43.572 --> 00:21:44.698
Coming back where?

00:21:44.698 --> 00:21:47.200
To class. He’s been
absent for a while.

00:21:47.520 --> 00:21:48.923
I’m just worried.

00:21:49.328 --> 00:21:50.620
What happened to him?

00:21:52.039 --> 00:21:54.124
Or is he just really busy
with his shoots now?

00:21:58.962 --> 00:22:00.547
All right, I’ll go ahead.

00:22:07.012 --> 00:22:09.514
But Kino, don’t neglect yourself,

00:22:09.514 --> 00:22:12.204
don’t neglect your studies, okay?

00:22:12.678 --> 00:22:15.514
Being a director is
still your real dream, right?

00:22:18.545 --> 00:22:21.674
The question is, do I
even want to be an actor?

00:22:21.902 --> 00:22:24.863
But you also know
I’d still choose studying.

00:22:24.863 --> 00:22:26.281
And you better!

00:22:26.281 --> 00:22:28.116
If you dare mess up your studies,

00:22:28.116 --> 00:22:29.951
I’ll really get mad.

00:22:29.951 --> 00:22:31.161
Study first. I promise.

00:22:31.161 --> 00:22:32.496
- Promise?
- I promise.

00:22:53.683 --> 00:22:54.704
Via!

00:22:56.144 --> 00:22:57.145
You’re here.

00:22:57.771 --> 00:22:59.081
Did you text me?

00:22:59.106 --> 00:23:00.023
Sorry, my phone was
low on battery,

00:23:00.023 --> 00:23:01.188
so I couldn’t reply.

00:23:01.287 --> 00:23:02.747
So, have you eaten yet?

00:23:03.485 --> 00:23:04.903
How’s your class?

00:23:07.364 --> 00:23:08.868
I don’t have class today.
It’s tomorrow.

00:23:09.157 --> 00:23:10.450
Perfect timing, huh?

00:23:15.622 --> 00:23:17.416
You’re such a liar.

00:23:18.875 --> 00:23:20.836
Acting really does suit you.

00:23:37.850 --> 00:23:39.435
Via, I can explain.

00:23:40.689 --> 00:23:43.108
You’ve had so many
chances to explain,

00:23:44.192 --> 00:23:45.610
why didn’t you?

00:23:47.821 --> 00:23:49.322
What did I ever do to you?

00:23:53.034 --> 00:23:55.036
You made me look like an idiot.

00:23:55.494 --> 00:23:57.758
I kept asking questions
about your classes.

00:23:59.541 --> 00:24:01.555
Why did you lie to me? Tell me.

00:24:02.506 --> 00:24:03.805
What did I do to you?

00:24:07.090 --> 00:24:08.836
Nothing, Via.

00:24:10.302 --> 00:24:11.360
Nothing?

00:24:11.636 --> 00:24:12.703
So I did nothing wrong.

00:24:13.930 --> 00:24:15.307
Then why didn’t you tell me?

00:24:17.017 --> 00:24:18.560
Do you not trust me anymore?

00:24:20.854 --> 00:24:21.771
What else about you
is even real?

00:24:21.771 --> 00:24:23.106
Go on, tell me.

00:24:30.915 --> 00:24:31.916
Via, I’m sorry.

00:24:32.574 --> 00:24:35.368
I’m sorry because I didn’t
know how to tell you.

00:24:36.077 --> 00:24:37.412
How could you not know?

00:24:38.657 --> 00:24:42.202
I was scared you’d get
really mad and leave me.

00:24:46.588 --> 00:24:47.772
I have to admit,

00:24:47.797 --> 00:24:50.967
I can’t handle both acting
and school at the same time.

00:24:52.594 --> 00:24:55.096
That’s why my manager had me
stop attending school.

00:24:56.681 --> 00:24:58.391
They’ll just have me
attend film courses

00:24:58.391 --> 00:25:01.019
that fit my schedule.

00:25:01.895 --> 00:25:02.938
Via, I’m sorry.

00:25:03.845 --> 00:25:05.513
Sorry, I didn’t tell you sooner.

00:25:06.191 --> 00:25:09.611
I’m still thinking about whether
I’ll enroll next semester.

00:25:11.738 --> 00:25:14.407
I thought you were doing
this for your film degree?

00:25:16.284 --> 00:25:17.577
I thought you were doing this

00:25:17.577 --> 00:25:19.246
because you wanted
to be a director.

00:25:21.081 --> 00:25:23.708
I thought you didn’t
want to be an actor.

00:25:26.836 --> 00:25:28.672
Has all that changed now?

00:25:29.839 --> 00:25:30.844
Huh?

00:25:31.383 --> 00:25:34.928
Are you enjoying all the
attention they’re giving you?

00:25:36.054 --> 00:25:37.556
Via, it’s not like that.

00:25:37.556 --> 00:25:39.015
Okay? It’s not like that.

00:25:39.224 --> 00:25:40.266
So, what is it?

00:25:41.643 --> 00:25:43.603
Tell me, why?

00:25:45.063 --> 00:25:46.106
How?

00:25:47.315 --> 00:25:49.276
Kino, I want to
understand because

00:25:49.276 --> 00:25:51.194
I want to understand you.

00:25:59.160 --> 00:26:01.204
Via, let’s just talk later, okay?

00:26:01.913 --> 00:26:03.248
Why not now?

00:26:06.876 --> 00:26:08.837
I’m sorry, Via. I’m tired.

