@samanthavera:
Just a reminder, guys.

00:27:02.549 --> 00:27:05.719
My birthday’s on Sunday.
See you!

00:27:15.320 --> 00:27:16.988
Happy birthday!

00:27:16.988 --> 00:27:18.073
Thank you.

00:27:18.073 --> 00:27:20.825
- Happy birthday!
- Thank you, girls.

00:27:20.825 --> 00:27:22.077
Thank you for coming.

00:27:24.204 --> 00:27:26.164
Kalix is not here. Don’t worry.

00:27:27.832 --> 00:27:29.542
It’s not like
I’m looking for him.

00:27:30.627 --> 00:27:32.379
Not looking ‘cause
you don’t want to see him,

00:27:32.379 --> 00:27:34.506
or because you do want to?

00:27:34.506 --> 00:27:36.216
I said I’m not looking for him!

00:27:37.592 --> 00:27:39.094
So? Are you introducing
someone to us?

00:27:39.594 --> 00:27:41.054
I wouldn’t want
to waste my outfit.

